2009 TAG TEAM LEAGUE IN FRONT OF A LIVE AUDIENCE
THE DRAGONS
Ariel X x & Wenona
Combined HT:131"
Combined WT: 235lbs
Season Record:(3-0)
Franchise Record (3-4)
THE NINJAS
Vendetta & Isis Love
Combined HT:132"
Combined WT: 255lbs
Season Record:(3-0)
Franchise record (6-1)
Welcome to Ultimate Surrender's 2009 Tag Team League.
The Dragons vs The Ninjas. Four girls,
non-scripted, real tag team action.
Match up of the year! Both teams undefeated, both teams healthy. Both teams wanting to get the bye to the championship. Both with a huge history. Ariel X beat Vendetta for the season 7 Championship. Wenona put Isis out for 2 years with a leg injury the last time they met on the mat. Both team want this victory!
The Dragons: Ariel X is the current Ultimate Surrender Champion. Wenona is one of the strongest wrestlers on the roster with 20 submissions to her name. This teams endurance is legendary.
The Ninjas: Are pissed. Pissed that no one takes Isis seriously as a top wrestler. Pissed that Vendetta loss the Championship to Ariel X. Pissed That few people think they can win this match. Pissed that Wenona took out Isis for two years with a leg injury. Pissed! Never piss off a Ninja!
title: LIVE TAG TEAM LEAGUE The Dragons (3-0) vs The Ninjas (3-0)
